Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were found in an aristocrat's manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they perhaps from your world?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never seen so many of them in one place at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, as for their use...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by their shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nononononono.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they may look like that, but they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the water?! With these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This summer's hotter than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear about the summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Group trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They cancelled the trip to the Great Cathedral in Romalia, and we're going to the ocean instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, you've never seen the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, since I've always lived in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the beach at night! It's so mysterious and romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to walk the beach with me at night to gaze at the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with the Order of Perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you forgive him already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll only get full of himself if I forgive him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vacation's the perfect opportunity to fix relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! What are you doing, Kirche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd... I'd never let him go further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... a night time stroll along the beach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tiffa, what do you think of the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so blue... and big.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And salty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to go to a beach during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta?! Why are you here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even wearing a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to take care of Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. Those are {\i1}not{\i0\fscx50} {\r} swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those"? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real swimsuit should be more like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And like this down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this has to be more like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we enter the ocean, the Queen has a word to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen does?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thanks to Principal Osmond,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here to join the Tristain Magic\NAcademy's annual summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to get along with everyone here without consideration of status...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and let us enjoy the vacation together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to start things off,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all girls, change into what's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a real swimsuit looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this area, one must give prayer to the Spirit of Water before entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it is a tradition, there are special uniforms for the priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a Spirit of Water in the ocean, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we can't get in the ocean unless you change into those!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belly is totally exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wear something indecent like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to wear one, Your Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the students shall surely follow suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When in Romalia, do as Romalians do. {there is no Rome in this land, but there is Romalia. How's this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is to give prayer to the Spirit of Water, I will gladly change into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Princess is going to wear one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be wearing one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now begin the purification ritual for the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First splash each other with water to cleanse one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, start splashing each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring status, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so cheeky! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been happier to be alive than today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito. You come from a wonderful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more extreme ones than those, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then lets have them wear those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll call us the Order of Perverts, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't want to see it, Reinard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important ritual to offer prayer to the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:08:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us burn the sights of beautiful, innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pure girls offering their prayers to the Spirit onto our eyes together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:03.88,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're changing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the sake of the Spirit of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta... Aren't you getting full of yourself recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This keeps falling off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's an offering ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This view is glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit more to the right, Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine a lecherous intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Why did you make Tiffa wear that of all things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ah... I thought you looked good in that swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you want to go out for a stroll tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Louise, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next ritual makes use of a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The team that wins this ritual will don the true priestess' garments,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowed only to the chosen maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all for the Spirit of Water's prayer, so take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chosen maidens...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to see Tiffa in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll set things up so that she wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the whole picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I can see Tiffa in an amazing swimsuit, then I'm your man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm chosen as a true maiden, then I'm sure Saito would...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is a match, Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first match is Team Queen and Agnes vs. Team Tiffania and Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your eyes knotholes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was definitely in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word of the referees is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was definitely in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10-7! Team Tiffania and Siesta wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost due to your crappy judgement!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, Team Louise and Montmorency vs. Team Kirche and Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are doing it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10-9. Team Louise and Montmorency wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.93,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Team Kirche vs. Team Tiffania in tomorrow's final.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you would understand the mood more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem if we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito. L-Let's go for the walk, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm kind of busy right now, so later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even asked him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let him pick up where we left off last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was a shame that Kirche's team lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll finally be time for this tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean that that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the true maiden garment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Hard to believe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined this would be a swimsuit, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I've only seen this one in magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is beyond perversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sickos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get what you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're late! What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency. What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My leg's cramped up from using it too much yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sunburn hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulder's stiff from wearing something I'm not used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm busy healing everyone with my Water magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take part in the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So all four finalists are taking a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and a message from Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to be alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So come to the rocky stretch alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure no one sees you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To set up "alone time" by lying means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess people in this world become more open at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to scare you, Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sorry"? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Zerbst. What is it that you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,calling me out to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make a guess, but we are teacher and student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course, Principal Osmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this suit your tastes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I can't believe that Tiffa gave me a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew Tiffa loved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in your lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you guys trick us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you guys talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've been found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Do you feel like giving prayers to the Spirit of Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is a vacation, you guys went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, Malicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, since you have more breasts than someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry! We really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We swear we won't do it again, so forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left my wand at the inn, so there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that, everyone, look at our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the tide rising?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting better at it, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Miss Vallière?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I bumped into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to me, Siesta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Spirit of Water that appears once every thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary giant octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is blinded with rage since you all neglected the ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a joke. A joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa! Montmorency!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't do it, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Let go of those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an envi... I mean, horrible thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need is ha nowsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.38,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha's the only one with her wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you cast something stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Anything stronger would hurt the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Untie us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, look at the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can run along its leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'll save you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come save me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a useless familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I come from, this is how you eat octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'll all love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let those lechers see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...But we wanted to try these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tiffa's by far the best one in these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't stare at me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that one too big for Miss Vallière?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to get to see them in the true maiden garment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind dying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone else just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise. The octopus balls are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
